" Map ,p to promote variable assignment to let in rspec
map <leader>p :call PromoteToLet()<cr>
function! PromoteToLet()
  :normal! dd
  :exec '?^\s*describe\|fdescribe\|fcontext\|context\|RSpec\.describe\>'
  :normal! p
  :.s/\(\w\+\)\s\+=\s\+\(.*\)$/let(:\1) { \2 }/
  :normal ==
endfunction

